<!-- SERVICES -->
<section id="services">
  <p class="section-label">// What We Do</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Full-stack AI implementation.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">From environment setup to production automation — we handle the entire AI stack so your team can focus on building.</p>

  <div class="services-grid">
    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">&gt;_</div>
      <h3>Claude Code Setup</h3>
      <p>Full environment configuration — permissions, project context, custom commands, and terminal integration. Your developers get a coding co-pilot that actually understands your codebase from day one.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">⬡</div>
      <h3>MCP Server Implementation</h3>
      <p>We connect Claude to your tools — Slack, GitHub, Drive, Salesforce, Jira, databases, and more. Proper authentication, scoping, and data flow so Claude can read and act on your company's real information.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">{'{ }'}</div>
      <h3>API Integration</h3>
      <p>Custom Anthropic API integrations for your product or internal tools. Structured outputs, streaming, function calling, multi-turn conversations — built to your exact specifications.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">⟁</div>
      <h3>Agentic Workflows</h3>
      <p>Multi-step AI automations that handle real work: lead qualification, document processing, code review, support triage, data analysis, reporting. Claude does the job, not just the chat.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Automation Pipelines</h3>
      <p>End-to-end pipelines connecting AI to your business processes. Trigger-based workflows, webhook integrations, scheduled tasks, and real-time processing — all production-grade.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">▶</div>
      <h3>Training & Onboarding</h3>
      <p>Hands-on training for your team so they actually use what we build. Prompt engineering, Claude Code workflows, MCP best practices, and documentation your team will reference daily.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CLAWDBOT -->
<section id="clawdbot">
