  <h2 class="section-title">ClawdBot — your AI front desk.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">A custom AI voice agent that answers calls, books appointments, handles SMS, and qualifies leads — 24/7. Built and deployed for your business in days.</p>

  <div class="services-grid">
    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">☎</div>
      <h3>Custom ClawdBot Builds</h3>
      <p>We build AI voice agents tailored to your industry — real estate, dental, therapy, skincare, salons, and more. Custom scripts, personality, FAQs, and business logic so it sounds like your best employee.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">🔊</div>
      <h3>Voice AI Phone Answering</h3>
      <p>Never miss a call again. Your ClawdBot picks up every call, handles common questions, routes complex ones, and captures caller details — even at 2 AM on a Saturday.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">💬</div>
      <h3>SMS + Appointment Booking</h3>
      <p>Automated text conversations that qualify leads and book appointments directly into your calendar. No app downloads, no portals — just a text conversation that converts.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
