      <p>Want to offer AI phone answering under your own brand? We deploy full white-label ClawdBot instances with your branding, dashboard, and pricing — ready for you to resell.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW WE WORK -->
<section id="process">
  <p class="section-label">// How We Work</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Embedded first. Build second.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">We don't show up with a playbook. We learn your business from the inside, then architect a solution that actually fits.</p>

  <div class="process-timeline">
    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-marker">
        <span class="process-number">01</span>
        <div class="process-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-duration">Days 1–3</div>
        <h3>Discovery Embed</h3>
        <p>We spend 3 days inside your operation — on-site or remote. We shadow your team, map every tool, document every workflow, identify every bottleneck, and learn how your business actually runs. Not how you think it runs. How it <em>actually</em> runs.</p>
        <div class="process-details">
          <span>Tool & data flow audit</span>
          <span>Team workflow mapping</span>
          <span>Pain point identification</span>
          <span>Opportunity scoring</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-marker">
        <span class="process-number">02</span>
        <div class="process-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-duration">Days 4–5</div>
        <h3>Architecture & Planning</h3>
        <p>We take everything we learned and design your custom AI implementation plan — which MCP connections, what workflows to automate, where ClawdBot fits, what API integrations you need, and the exact order to build it all. You approve the blueprint before we write a line of code.</p>
        <div class="process-details">
          <span>Custom architecture design</span>
          <span>MCP connection map</span>
          <span>Workflow automation plan</span>
          <span>Implementation timeline</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-marker">
        <span class="process-number">03</span>
        <div class="process-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-duration">Weeks 2–3</div>
        <h3>Build & Deploy</h3>
        <p>We execute the plan — fast. Claude Code configured, MCP servers connected, ClawdBot deployed, automation pipelines live, API integrations wired up. Everything tested in your real environment with your real data before we call it done.</p>
        <div class="process-details">
          <span>Environment configuration</span>
          <span>Integration & automation build</span>
          <span>QA with real data</span>
          <span>Production deployment</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-marker">
        <span class="process-number">04</span>
      </div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-duration">Weeks 3–5</div>
        <h3>Launch, Train & Support</h3>
        <p>We train your team hands-on — not a slide deck, real working sessions. Then we stick around for 2 weeks post-launch to fix anything, tune workflows, and answer every question. You're never left figuring it out alone.</p>
        <div class="process-details">
          <span>Team training sessions</span>
          <span>Custom documentation</span>
          <span>2-week support window</span>
          <span>Optimization & tuning</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:3rem;">
    <p style="font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--light-gray);line-height:1.7;max-width:600px;">Infrastructure and hardware needs (dedicated machines, cloud resources, etc.) are scoped during discovery and billed separately at cost + 15%.</p>
  </div>
</section>

