<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq">
  <p class="section-label">// Questions</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked.</h2>

  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">What is Claude Code and why do I need it?</button>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <p>Claude Code is Anthropic's command-line tool for agentic AI coding. It lets your developers delegate tasks to Claude directly from the terminal — editing files, running commands, searching codebases, and managing git. Most teams need help configuring it properly for their specific stack, permissions, and workflows. That's what we do.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">What are MCP servers?</button>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <p>MCP (Model Context Protocol) servers let Claude connect directly to your existing tools — Slack, GitHub, Google Drive, Salesforce, databases, and more. Instead of copy-pasting context into chat, Claude can read and act on your real company data. We handle setup, authentication, and data flow configuration.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">How long does implementation take?</button>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <p>Most implementations are done in 1–2 weeks. A basic Claude Code + MCP setup takes 3–5 days. Full enterprise implementations with custom workflows and automation pipelines take 2–3 weeks. We move fast because we've done this before.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">What tools can you connect?</button>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <p>Virtually anything your team uses: Slack, GitHub, Google Drive, Calendar, Gmail, Salesforce, Jira, Asana, Notion, PostgreSQL, MySQL, Stripe, HubSpot, Linear, Figma, and many more. If an MCP server exists for it — or needs to be built — we handle it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">What is ClawdBot?</button>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <p>ClawdBot is a custom AI voice agent that answers your business phone, handles SMS conversations, books appointments, and qualifies leads — 24/7. We build and deploy ClawdBot instances tailored to your industry with custom scripts, personality, and business logic. We also offer full white-label deployments so you can resell AI phone answering under your own brand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">Do you build custom automations?</button>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <p>Yes. Beyond setup, we design and build agentic AI workflows — automated pipelines where Claude handles multi-step business processes like lead qualification, document processing, code review, support triage, data analysis, and reporting. Production-grade, not demos.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">What's included in the lead scraping add-on?</button>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <p>We build custom lead scraping pipelines that pull verified business data — names, phone numbers, emails, addresses — from Google Maps, industry directories, and public databases. Data is cleaned, deduplicated, and delivered in ready-to-use formats. Thousands of targeted leads for your outreach, not junk data from a broker.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">Why is this expensive?</button>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <p>Because figuring this out yourself takes your team weeks or months of trial and error. We do it in days because it's all we do. You're buying speed, certainty, and a working system — not hours on a clock. The ROI is immediate.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

